HEADWORD: Kidderminster
<hw>Kid"der*min`ster</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A kind of
ingrain carpeting, named from the English town where formerly most of it
was manufactured.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

